{
  "stem": "3988.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I worked as-- we worked in a forest, you know-- cut down trees to make roads, expressways, you know, for the German army can go from one place to the next place and, you know, helped build expressways, you know.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And stayed in the camps.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in that, you know, we had our civilian clothes, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no uniforms then, just the clothes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to-- from day-- every day, six days a week, you know, we went to the camps.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and when the camps-- you know, we used to get our ration-- you know, a piece of bread, a slice of bread, and a cup of soup, a bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was our daily food, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember in one of the camps, we used to get a little loaf of bread-- you know, a little small loaf of bread.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's supposed to last for five days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we ate it up, you know, in one time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the next four days, I didn't eat.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have no bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even we-- I could save a piece of bread, but what I'm going do with it?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Where I'm going to put it?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know, somebody going to steal it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I might as well ate it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you know, for the next four days, we didn't eat no bread-- just get a bowl of soup.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and in the camp, I remember, they kept a storage.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kept like, the beets, the carrots, you know, potatoes-- they kept in the cellar, you know, because that's [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were-- had little windows.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one time, at night, I tied my pants down with a piece of rope, you know, here-- tie them down.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
